                    <p class="card-text">Complete Independence: Fully independent from the utility grid, ideal for remote or rural locations without reliable grid access.</p>
                    <p class="card-text">Uninterrupted Power: Perfect for areas prone to frequent power outages, providing consistent energy availability.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Hybrid-Grid Card -->
