                    <p class="card-text">Best of Both Worlds: Merges the benefits of both on-grid and off-grid systems, featuring connection to the utility grid with added battery backup.</p>
                    <p class="card-text">Enhanced Self-Reliance: Ensures power availability even during grid failures or in low sunlight conditions.</p>
                    <p class="card-text">Flexibility and Security: Offers superior flexibility and energy security, making it a robust choice for varying power needs.</p>
